metadata.name: In the Beginning
metadata.description:
The creation of this AI artwork NFT was inspired by :

The BIBLE - Genesis 1:1 - In the beginning. God created the heavens and the earth.

The Metadata of this NFT contains hidden properties that include valuable information such as the Genesis verse, the Creation Source, and other helpful data permanently stored in the blockchain.  
 
I used the ASCII art signature as a trademark for MetaFeat artworks on the  Ethereum smart contracts, which you can find in Etherscan.

"This is the next chapter in artwork creation."
